node.text:
For a wonderfully unique stay in Tokyo, look no further than @tokyostationhotel. This hotel is filled with so much history and charm, you could walk it’s halls and have walked entire length of Tokyo Tower while reading about the hotel throughout the years on your way. 🗼

Beyond the award-winning breakfast buffet, you'll find a few more charms, such as the ability to people-watch commuters below at Tokyo Station or watch the trains pass by from your dinner table. Be sure to save this hotel for a special occasion or at least stop by for their beautiful high tea. 🫖 #TokyoStationHotel #Tokyo 🇯🇵
